p: The samples analyzed in this study belong to the collection from the Laboratory of Flavivirus, IOC/FIOCRUZ, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil, and were obtained through the passive surveillance system from an ongoing Project approved by resolution number CAAE 90249218.6.1001.5248 from the Oswaldo Cruz Foundation Ethical Committee in Research (CEP 2.998.362), Ministry of Health-Brazil. Samples were chosen anonymously, based on the laboratorial results.
